---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Katie d'Autremont, a licensed clinical social worker specializing in anxiety, depression, and life transitions.">
  <section class="py-3xl px-lg">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-xl text-center">About Katie</h1>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-xl items-start">
        <!-- Photo placeholder -->
        <div class="md:col-span-1">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-cream-dark rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-warm-gray">
            <span class="text-sm">Photo</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-md">
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal">
            I'm Katie d'Autremont, a licensed clinical social worker with a private practice focused on helping people navigate anxiety, depression, relational challenges, and life transitions.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal-light">
            My approach to therapy is rooted in curiosity and collaboration. I believe that meaningful change happens when people feel genuinely seen and supported — and when they're ready to do the work that growth requires.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal-light">
            Over the years, I've found that the insights from therapy extend far beyond the session room. That's what led me to start writing and creating resources for people who want to engage with this work on their own terms — whether or not they're in therapy.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal-light">
            When I'm not working, you'll probably find me with Goose, my dog, who has taught me more about presence and patience than any textbook.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Credentials -->
      <div class="mt-3xl pt-xl border-t border-cream-dark">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-lg text-center">Credentials & Training</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-lg text-center">
          <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">Licensed Clinical Social Worker</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-gray mt-xs">LCSW</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-lg rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal">Private Practice</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-gray mt-xs">Be Balanced Counseling</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-warm-gray text-center mt-lg">
          Additional credentials and training details can be added here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
